item.title: CVE-2017-8175|2024-08-05T16:27:22.932Z -- huawei%20technologies%20co.%2C%20ltd. -- vicky-al00a%2Cvictoria-al00a%2Cwarsaw-al00
item.description: The Bastet of some Huawei mobile phones with software earlier than Vicky-AL00AC00B167 versions, earlier than Victoria-AL00AC00B167 versions, earlier than Warsaw-AL00C00B191 versions has an insufficient input validation vulnerability due to the lack of parameter validation. An attacker may trick a user into installing a malicious APP. The APP can modify specific parameter to cause system reboot.
